a quarter off of.

25:40.123 --> 25:42.633
But I hadn't really noticed,
I have to tell you.

25:44.169 --> 25:48.129
Oh, sometimes I forget
how good of a liar you are.

25:48.715 --> 25:50.625
I love you.

25:54.512 --> 25:56.892
I love you so much.

26:01.394 --> 26:03.404
You know that, right?

27:25.103 --> 27:28.113
- Good morning.
- Good morning.

27:32.986 --> 27:35.696
- Good morning, hon.
- Good morning.

27:37.532 --> 27:39.162
Thank you.

27:39.951 --> 27:43.251
Anna, we'd like you to stay here
with us in our guest house.

27:43.955 --> 27:46.365
We'd like you to take time off of work.

27:46.541 --> 27:48.041
We'll pay you whatever you were making.

27:48.209 --> 27:51.669
We'll get you a car so you don't feel
trapped. Come and go as you please.

27:51.838 --> 27:53.128
- Are you serious?
- Yeah.

27:53.298 --> 27:55.508
We talked about it.
We feel more comfortable...

27:55.675 --> 27:58.845
- ...knowing you're here most of the time.
- And knowing that you're safe.

27:59.012 --> 28:01.102
It's just... I think Mike...

28:01.264 --> 28:03.984
Anna, Mike hurt you.

28:04.851 --> 28:07.191
And he's not gonna be around anymore.

28:07.354 --> 28:09.444
Not for a very long time.

28:09.647 --> 28:13.317
Now, you are doing
this incredible thing for us.

28:13.485 --> 28:15.695
It's the least we can do.

28:16.696 --> 28:19.656
Let us do something nice for you, okay?

28:21.868 --> 28:23.998
- Okay.
- Okay.

28:25.955 --> 28:27.955
Thank you.

28:57.821 --> 29:01.951
Well, she is now officially
better than me in yoga.

29:02.117 --> 29:04.487
Well, she's 10 weeks pregnant.
Give it another five weeks...

29:04.661 --> 29:06.871
...you'll be able to take her down.

29:07.038 --> 29:09.868
Because yoga's all about who wins, right?

29:10.041 --> 29:13.671
She says it's got her body going crazy.

29:13.837 --> 29:16.627
For sex, for men.

29:16.798 --> 29:18.048
I guess it's the hormones.

29:18.258 --> 29:19.798
Anything from the boyfriend?

29:20.301 --> 29:22.721
No. Nothing.

29:22.887 --> 29:27.347
He just shipped out
without even contacting her.

29:28.059 --> 29:30.229
I'm glad he's gone.

29:30.603 --> 29:33.063
- Ready for the associate's dinner?
- All set.

29:33.273 --> 29:35.823
Laura, sweetie, come on, let's go.

29:35.984 --> 29:37.614
I'm coming!

29:37.777 --> 29:40.067
Sometime tonight, sweetheart.

29:50.415 --> 29:52.455
Oh, my God.

29:52.625 --> 29:54.535
You look like a movie star.

29:56.212 --> 29:57.422
You like?

29:58.006 --> 30:00.836
I love that dress.

30:01.509 --> 30:04.099
You look absolutely stunning.

30:06.764 --> 30:07.854
Can I take your picture?

30:08.475 --> 30:10.225
All right.

30:10.393 --> 30:12.023
Listen, you have both of our cell numbers.

30:12.187 --> 30:14.647
And we'll be home by midnight.

30:15.857 --> 30:18.607
Okay, 1.

30:21.696 --> 30:23.196
I'll get the car.

30:23.364 --> 30:25.204
So beautiful.

30:28.536 --> 30:30.406
It's amazing the way he is with you.

30:30.580 --> 30:32.040
You are so lucky.

30:33.500 --> 30:35.630
Thank you. Thank you, Anna.

30:35.793 --> 30:37.003
And you have a good night.

30:37.170 --> 30:40.170
- You too. Have fun.
- All right. We will.

30:41.925 --> 30:43.045
"Today...

30:43.218 --> 30:44.718
...I am happy.

30:46.721 --> 30:50.311
I am in control of my life.

30:50.725 --> 30:54.935
I will experience the joy of pure love."

33:10.782 --> 33:12.032
Sorry.

33:12.200 --> 33:14.450
I was watching TV.

33:14.619 --> 33:16.749
- I guess I fell asleep.
- No problem.

33:16.913 --> 33:18.543
I fall asleep there all the time.

33:19.082 --> 33:20.582
I'd like a cup of coffee.

33:22.085 --> 33:24.375
Doctor says I'm allowed one cup a day.

33:24.921 --> 33:26.511
Okay.

33:30.385 --> 33:34.135
- One cup.
- Thank you.

33:35.682 --> 33:38.812
- God, it's so old.
- Miss Havisham.

33:39.477 --> 33:42.057
She's not old, she's ancient.

33:42.397 --> 33:44.977
I was never really a cat person,
but Laura loves her.

33:45.525 --> 33:49.235
All these years, she treated that cat
just like she was her baby.

33:49.612 --> 33:51.162
But when the real baby comes...

33:51.322 --> 33:53.912
...we'll have to see how old
Miss Havisham reacts then, huh?

33:55.785 --> 33:58.035
I told Laura she's lucky to have you.

34:00.081 --> 34:04.961
A husband who really loves his wife.

34:05.128 --> 34:07.258
Well, I like to think
that I'm the lucky one.

34:07.422 --> 34:09.762
I knew you would say something like that.

34:15.221 --> 34:16.261
Do you wanna feel?

34:18.808 --> 34:20.938
Here. Give me your hand.

34:21.101 --> 34:22.562
I'll show you what it feels like.

34:22.728 --> 34:25.228
Wait, I shouldn't say "it."

34:25.398 --> 34:27.148
It's not an it.

34:27.315 --> 34:28.476
He's your baby boy.

34:30.277 --> 34:31.777
You think it's a boy?

34:31.946 --> 34:33.946
I know it's a boy.

34:34.114 --> 34:35.155
I can feel him.

34:39.829 --> 34:42.539
He isn't even an inch long yet.

34:43.498 --> 34:47.339
But you can feel where
my tummy's starting to change.

34:48.004 --> 34:49.014
Feel that?

34:49.922 --> 34:51.922
How it's harder?

34:52.091 --> 34:54.221
Yeah, yeah. Yeah, I can feel it.

34:54.427 --> 34:55.507
He's growing.

34:55.678 --> 34:58.508
Changing every day.

35:08.983 --> 35:11.863
Can I admit something to you?

35:13.529 --> 35:16.909
It's a little weird that
I'm pregnant with your baby.

35:18.201 --> 35:21.251
That you're inside of me...

35:21.412 --> 35:23.162
...in that way.

35:23.331 --> 35:26.291
Yeah, yeah, that is strange, isn't it?

35:26.918 --> 35:28.128
Yeah.

35:28.294 --> 35:30.134
But we're grateful for that.

35:30.296 --> 35:33.716
Because without you,
we couldn't do any of this.

35:33.883 --> 35:35.843
I like it.

35:39.972 --> 35:41.602
Yep.

35:43.559 --> 35:46.099
Hey, listen, next week we're
having our annual charity event...

35:46.270 --> 35:47.810
...here at the house. You should join us.

35:47.980 --> 35:50.070
- What's it for?
- We like to raise money...

35:50.233 --> 35:52.533
...for the Boys and Girls Club of America.

35:52.819 --> 35:56.239
You're amazing. Yes, I will come.

36:15.633 --> 36:17.593
What's so important?

36:22.598 --> 36:24.598
Good to see you too.

36:24.767 --> 36:26.597
I missed you, baby.

36:26.769 --> 36:29.269
I'm so glad you miss me.

36:30.815 --> 36:32.185
You look nice.

36:33.609 --> 36:38.609
I mean, living up there in that beautiful
big house, that must be nice.

36:38.781 --> 36:42.121
Did you know that you have
their only embryo?

36:42.285 --> 36:46.325
- It's a baby now.
- And they don't have any more.

36:46.831 --> 36:48.711
And in the eyes of the law...

36:48.875 --> 36:52.545
...since it's inside of you,
it belongs to us.

36:53.379 --> 36:57.969
We can decide to keep it for ourselves
anytime we want.

36:58.134 --> 37:01.304
- But I... I thought...
- Don't think.

37:01.679 --> 37:03.889
It's not your thing, baby.

37:04.056 --> 37:06.226
I'm the brains on this.

37:06.684 --> 37:08.944
You're just the uterus.

37:16.193 --> 37:18.403
So here's what you're gonna do.

37:18.571 --> 37:21.991
Every single month, you're gonna say...

37:22.158 --> 37:25.698
...that you're changing your mind,
and you're keeping it.

37:25.870 --> 37:27.620
And they'll pay.

37:27.788 --> 37:29.958
Maybe four grand, maybe more.

37:30.124 --> 37:31.834
Mike.

37:33.252 --> 37:36.342
They've been really good to me.

37:37.214 --> 37:40.384
John really wants to be a father.

37:46.849 --> 37:48.639
Does he?

37:49.685 --> 37:51.685
Does he really?

38:18.506 --> 38:20.586
You're into him.

38:22.301 --> 38:26.181
What do you think is gonna happen, Anna?

38:29.308 --> 38:33.268
You'll live happily ever after
with him in that big house?

38:36.399 --> 38:38.609
He doesn't care about you.

38:38.985 --> 38:41.735
You are like a cow to him.

38:44.115 --> 38:47.615
I'll do it. I'll do it, Mike. I'll do it.

38:48.244 --> 38:50.124
I know you will.

38:50.287 --> 38:52.497
I'll do it. I'll tell them.

38:58.671 --> 39:01.261
I'll do it for you, baby.

39:02.425 --> 39:05.135
Anything you want.

39:19.900 --> 39:24.700
It's from the firm. And tell Laura
she absolutely tops herself...

39:24.864 --> 39:27.374
- ...every time you guys do this.
- I'll do that. Thanks.

39:27.533 --> 39:30.583
Nobody knows this yet,
but Grafton Industries...

39:30.745 --> 39:34.535
...is unofficially
floating settlement offers.

39:34.707 --> 39:37.417
- You're not gonna settle with them?
- You kidding me?

39:37.585 --> 39:40.125
All this time, you've been telling me
we had them by the balls.

39:40.296 --> 39:42.166
I just wasn't sure.

39:42.339 --> 39:43.719
But now I am.

39:44.508 --> 39:47.298
This is gonna lock up partner
for you, John.

39:47.470 --> 39:49.010
You take them to trial.

39:49.180 --> 39:50.560
Gut them like a fish.

39:50.973 --> 39:52.733
I'll do that.

40:02.943 --> 40:04.493
Look, I was talking to Anna earlier.

40:04.653 --> 40:06.953
I didn't realise she was
your second cousin, man.

40:07.114 --> 40:08.994
- She is amazing.
- Todd, she's 21.

40:09.575 --> 40:11.735
My calculation, that's...

40:11.911 --> 40:14.001
That's legal plus three, right?

40:14.705 --> 40:17.785
I'm just checking with you. You wouldn't
mind if I asked her out, would you?

40:17.958 --> 40:19.498
No. You can ask her out.

40:24.340 --> 40:26.130
Normally, this is the part
of the evening...

40:26.300 --> 40:28.930
...where John asks all of you
to reach for your chequebooks.

40:29.762 --> 40:33.102
And I'm sure he'll manage
to get that in still...

40:33.724 --> 40:35.524
...but first, I wanted everyone to know...

40:35.684 --> 40:40.314
...how important the Boys and Girls
Clubs of America is to us.

40:40.481 --> 40:42.691
Especially to my husband.

40:42.858 --> 40:46.068
John loves children, and they love him.

40:46.278 --> 40:48.278
Thank you, John.

40:49.573 --> 40:51.623
I'd also like...

40:55.996 --> 40:59.706
I'd also like to thank all of you here...

40:59.875 --> 41:01.745
...for coming tonight and...

41:03.963 --> 41:05.513
Thank you.

41:05.714 --> 41:07.264
Thank you.

41:09.093 --> 41:10.683
Now you can all take out your chequebooks.

41:16.058 --> 41:18.058
Is that the dress you gave her?

41:18.227 --> 41:20.097
No. It's not.

41:20.271 --> 41:22.231
You want me to go talk to her?

41:22.398 --> 41:25.068
No, I will.

41:29.280 --> 41:30.700
Excuse me, gentlemen.

41:32.283 --> 41:34.373
- Anna.
- What's the matter?

41:34.535 --> 41:35.945
That's not the dress I gave you.

41:38.497 --> 41:40.537
God, I'm so sorry.

41:40.708 --> 41:43.338
It's just, the one that
you gave me didn't really fit.

41:44.128 --> 41:48.378
I was gonna ask you,
but you were so busy with the party.

41:49.633 --> 41:51.763
I can... I can go change...

41:51.927 --> 41:55.177
- ...right now.
- No, it's fine.

41:56.015 --> 41:57.925
You look great.

42:08.527 --> 42:10.397
Thank you for staying late.
I appreciate it.

42:10.571 --> 42:13.871
- Thank you. Thanks.
- Thank you.

42:46.774 --> 42:49.324
Well, no one fell in the pool.

42:49.485 --> 42:50.895
The rain stayed away.

42:51.946 --> 42:54.106
I'd call that a win.

42:54.323 --> 42:56.333
I found it in your record collection.

43:00.579 --> 43:02.459
Where's Laura?

43:02.623 --> 43:05.043
Oh, yeah, she crashed about an hour ago.

43:05.251 --> 43:07.841
Has to catch a flight
at 6 in the morning for work.

43:08.003 --> 43:09.843
So how'd our little story hold up?

43:12.007 --> 43:14.297
It was great.

43:14.468 --> 43:16.468
I was acting out a part.

43:17.263 --> 43:20.223
I had a secret in me that no one knew.

43:22.059 --> 43:23.139
Except you.

43:25.354 --> 43:27.024
You know everybody loves you?

43:27.439 --> 43:30.399
- Shut up.
- I'm serious.

43:30.776 --> 43:34.196
It made me think that I made
a good choice for the baby.

43:35.739 --> 43:38.409
Well, I thought that we were
the ones that made the choice.

43:38.742 --> 43:40.202
I could've said no.

43:40.828 --> 43:42.198
True.

43:43.706 --> 43:45.826
You're gonna make a great dad.

43:47.459 --> 43:50.879
Well, I'm glad it was you.

43:58.721 --> 44:03.271
I am gonna take a bath before bed.

44:09.106 --> 44:12.066
Thank you for everything, John.

44:52.149 --> 44:53.649
Is everything okay?

44:54.109 --> 44:56.989
Something's knocking
against the guest house.

46:42.593 --> 46:44.553
Is there coffee?

46:47.514 --> 46:48.684
Yeah. Coming right up.

46:50.058 --> 46:51.638
When does Laura get home?

46:51.852 --> 46:53.652
Tuesday.

46:58.859 --> 47:00.859
So, look, about last night...

47:07.576 --> 47:09.196
Todd Decker, he was...

47:09.369 --> 47:10.659
He was asking about you.

47:11.580 --> 47:16.040
The guy in the Grey suit? You know,
he was staring at me all night.

47:16.210 --> 47:17.840
Had to be uncomfortable for you.

47:18.795 --> 47:21.215
Can't blame a person for staring.

47:21.381 --> 47:24.221
It just means they like what they see.

47:25.260 --> 47:28.310
Actually, I prefer older guys.

47:29.264 --> 47:30.564
I always have.

47:30.724 --> 47:33.394
Mike was the youngest guy I ever dated.

47:33.560 --> 47:36.730
- Is that your phone?
- They'll leave a message.

47:38.398 --> 47:40.068
So I have to go into the office today.

47:40.234 --> 47:41.614
- On a Sunday?
- Yeah.

47:41.777 --> 47:44.567
I got an important deposition.
You can order out.

47:44.738 --> 47:46.158
I'm not gonna be back until late.

47:56.959 --> 47:59.629
How about we go out to the lake house?

47:59.795 --> 48:02.205
Just you and I, a weekend
before the baby comes.

48:02.381 --> 48:04.221
As soon as you get back from Houston.

48:04.383 --> 48:05.763
I'd like that.

48:05.926 --> 48:08.046
John, you're not gonna like this...

48:08.220 --> 48:10.430
...but Chef Folse wants me out here
tomorrow as well.

48:11.765 --> 48:14.725
- You're right. I don't like it.
- Should I say no?

48:15.269 --> 48:17.439
Should I just come home now?

48:18.021 --> 48:20.441
No, go ahead and stay. It's okay.

48:25.028 --> 48:28.118
- Hey.
- I hope you're sitting down.

48:29.116 --> 48:32.866
Chef Folse is offering me
a major promotion.

48:33.036 --> 48:34.036
Really?

48:34.204 --> 48:36.584
That's the reason he brought me down,
so he could offer me...

48:36.748 --> 48:39.708
- ...the CEO position.
- Congratulations.

48:42.254 --> 48:43.844
But I thought we talked about, you know...

48:44.006 --> 48:45.836
We have six months before the baby's born.

48:46.008 --> 48:49.298
I told him I could run the company while
we look for a permanent replacement.

48:49.469 --> 48:50.849
Why not just turn it down, sweetheart?

48:51.013 --> 48:52.063
I think I should take it...

48:52.222 --> 48:55.142
...even if it is only for six months.
But that's assuming you agree.

48:55.476 --> 48:57.806
I mean, I'd have to spend
a few days a month up here.

48:57.978 --> 48:59.728
But that wouldn't be
until later in the year.

48:59.896 --> 49:01.566
And you could come up for some weekends.

49:02.399 --> 49:03.819
Babe, are you happy for me?

49:03.984 --> 49:07.204
- I really wanna do this.
- Yeah, no, sweetheart. Definitely.

49:07.362 --> 49:09.532
I'm... I'm definitely happy for you.

49:09.740 --> 49:10.950
- It's unbelievable.
- Yeah?

49:11.116 --> 49:13.576
And you like spending time
with Anna, right?

49:15.162 --> 49:17.662
She might even have
a little thing for you.

49:17.873 --> 49:19.373
It's cute. Whatever.

49:19.541 --> 49:21.881
I mean, you're a big boy,
you can handle a little attention.

49:22.044 --> 49:24.054
Just congratulate me.

49:25.672 --> 49:27.802
- Jesus. What the...?
- What?

49:27.966 --> 49:31.796
No, congratulations, sweetheart.
I am so proud of you.

49:33.138 --> 49:34.138
I love you.

49:34.681 --> 49:36.311
I'll see you tomorrow.

49:36.475 --> 49:38.475
I love you too, babe.

51:04.229 --> 51:05.899
Anna!

51:07.482 --> 51:10.112
- Hi, John.
- What are you doing?

51:11.695 --> 51:12.945
Look, do you see this?

51:13.113 --> 51:14.873
This is me and Laura.
She is my wife, okay?

51:15.031 --> 51:18.541
This is our home.
Do you not understand that?

51:19.077 --> 51:20.827
I don't wanna have to say anything to her.

51:21.455 --> 51:23.995
Maybe I should go.

51:24.166 --> 51:27.376
No, wait, hold on. No, no. Please, please.

51:27.544 --> 51:29.634
Okay, look.

51:29.796 --> 51:34.256
Maybe... Maybe I said something
to encourage you in all this.

51:34.426 --> 51:36.846
And if I did do that, then I am sorry.

51:38.764 --> 51:40.394
Hello!

51:40.557 --> 51:43.557
- Hey.
- Hi.

51:43.727 --> 51:46.227
Didn't wanna wait until tomorrow,
so I grabbed the next flight.

51:46.396 --> 51:49.606
Good. That's... That's good.
Congratulations on everything.

51:49.775 --> 51:51.565
Hello, Laura.

51:56.656 --> 51:59.986
Laura just got a promotion at her company.

52:01.661 --> 52:04.041
Well, it's only until the baby comes.

52:04.206 --> 52:06.666
- How are you?
- Everything is fine.

52:07.834 --> 52:11.924
- Welcome home.
- It's good to be back.

52:12.088 --> 52:13.298
It's good to have you back.

52:50.460 --> 52:52.250
Hey, baby.

53:09.729 --> 53:10.729
Is anybody home?

53:13.233 --> 53:15.243
Anybody wanna make me a goddamn quiche?

53:15.402 --> 53:17.072
Mike, stop it!

53:19.364 --> 53:22.584
You're drunk. Okay? I was gonna call you.

53:25.912 --> 53:29.082
Before they find out
this whole thing's a scam...

53:29.291 --> 53:31.921
...you're gonna tell them
that you changed your mind.

53:32.085 --> 53:33.795
- You'll get them to give you money.
- No.

53:33.962 --> 53:35.712
Shut up!

53:37.090 --> 53:39.430
You're gonna take that money.

53:40.135 --> 53:43.755
And you and I are heading to Arizona...

53:44.139 --> 53:46.059
...because there is a guy there...

53:46.224 --> 53:49.024
...that's gonna give us another $15,000...

53:49.185 --> 53:54.065
...for a nice, new baby.

53:59.321 --> 54:01.071
If you don't...

54:01.907 --> 54:03.617
...I'm gonna come back here later...

54:04.492 --> 54:08.462
...and I'm gonna tell Laura and John...

54:08.622 --> 54:10.462
...you wanted to take
their last baby from them.

54:10.999 --> 54:12.459
No.

54:12.626 --> 54:14.036
They'll hate you.

54:20.592 --> 54:22.552
Clean this up.

54:54.417 --> 54:56.167
Here you go.

55:20.986 --> 55:21.986
Hey! Hey!

55:22.529 --> 55:25.239
Get... Get back here!

55:39.462 --> 55:42.302
Leave a message
and I'll call you right back.

55:42.465 --> 55:44.175
God.

55:44.342 --> 55:47.052
It's so goddamn typical of you.

55:47.220 --> 55:49.560
Some asshole buys you some fancy shit...

55:49.723 --> 55:52.183
...and you fall head over heels for him.

55:52.350 --> 55:54.230
Call me.

55:55.937 --> 55:58.727
Stupid bitch.

56:49.866 --> 56:51.446
Yeah.

56:52.494 --> 56:54.374
You're the brains, Mike.

57:15.225 --> 57:18.685
I am happy.

57:20.021 --> 57:23.441
I am in control...

57:23.608 --> 57:25.938
...of my life.

57:26.736 --> 57:30.696
I feel the joy...

57:30.865 --> 57:33.905
...of pure love.

57:51.386 --> 57:54.426
Hi, this is Laura Taylor.
Leave a message, and I'll...

57:57.642 --> 57:59.232
I can't hold the room. I'm sorry.

